list.name: Jmeter Test Annotations
list.query: select text from events where $timeFilter AND application = '$jmeterappname'

targets.query: SELECT mean("maxActiveThreads") FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname' GROUP BY time(10s) fill(0)
SELECT  count("respTime")/$aggregation FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname' GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null)
SELECT last("maxActiveThreads") FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname' GROUP BY "maxActiveThreads" fill(0)
SELECT  count("respTime")/$aggregation FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[aggregation]]s) fill(null)
SELECT  count("respTime") FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname'
SELECT 1 - sum("errCount")/count("respTime") FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname'
SELECT sum("errCount")/count("respTime") FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname'

SELECT count(respTime) as Samples, percentile(respTime, 90) as "90%",percentile(respTime, 95) as "95%",percentile(respTime, 99) as "99%", mean(respTime) as Avg, min(respTime) as Min, median(respTime) as Median, max(respTime) as Max, (sum(errCount)/count(respTime)) as "Error Rate" FROM "requestsMetrics"  WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname' AND testType = 'Baseline' GROUP BY requestName order by asc
SELECT  count("errCount")/$aggregation FROM "requestsMetrics" WHERE $timeFilter AND projectName='$jmeterappname' GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null)

SELECT 100-mean("usage_idle") as "cpu.mean", 100-percentile("usage_idle",5) as "cpu.perc95", 100-min("usage_idle") as "cpu.max" FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND $timeFilter  GROUP BY "host", appSubname fill(null)
SELECT max("load1"), mean("load1"), percentile("load1",95) as perc95 FROM "system" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY  "host", appSubname fill(null)
SELECT 100-max("usage_idle") FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)
SELECT max("usage_user") FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)
SELECT max("usage_iowait") FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)
targets.target: SELECT max("usage_user") FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)

SELECT max("usage_idle") FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host" fill(null)

SELECT max("OC") - max("OU") as "old.free.min", max("OC") as "old.cap.max", max("OU") as "old.used.max", mean("OU") as "old.used.mean", max("MU") as "meta.used.max", mean("MU") as "meta.used.mean", max("EU") as "eden.used.max", mean("EU") as "eden.used.mean" FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY host, appSubname fill(null)

SELECT max("YGC")-min("YGC") as "young.gcs", max("YGCT")-min("YGCT") as "young.total.secs", ((max("YGCT")-min("YGCT")) * 1000) / (max("YGC")-min("YGC"))  as "young.mean.ms", max("FGC")-min("FGC") as "full.gcs", max("FGCT")-min("FGCT") as "full.total.secs", ((max("FGCT")-min("FGCT")) * 1000) / (max("FGC")-min("FGC"))  as "full.mean.ms" FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY host, appSubname fill(null)
SELECT max("OC") FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host, appSubname fill(null)
SELECT max("OU") FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host, appSubname fill(null)
SELECT max("EC") FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host, appSubname fill(null)
SELECT max("EU") FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host, appSubname fill(null)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("FGCT"),10s)*1000 FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host, appSubname fill(null)
SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("YGCT"),10s)*1000 FROM "heap" WHERE "host" =~ /$hostsRegEx/ AND appSubname =~ /$appSubname/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host, appSubname fill(null)
